amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;start=20&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p>Working closely with Andreu Lacondeguy and other RC athletes, the goal was to create a mid-top shoe with the added protection that comes with that. But the shoe also had to retain excellent feel at the pedal and look the part.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/U_PdYf8vU9o?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6.jpg\" alt=\"Ride Concepts Vice Mid shoe features\" width=\"1200\" height=\"927\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6-297x229.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/04103347/Ride-Concepts-Vice-Mid-MTB-bmx-shoe-Andreu-Lacondeguy-signature-color-6-800x618.jpg 800